Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:13.32,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,通称TSMも　本日開業十周年記念の年を迎えました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there is something we must never forget.
