Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a meaning no matter how sad and painful it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:27.74,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,悲しい事　辛い事にも　きっと意味はあるんだって
